{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fa0f6c2eeb","title":"再论革命的怀疑一切──砸碎形而上学的谬论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52d51c0a89","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":12,"articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"373678c6e0","name":"清华大学东方红南下革命串联队先锋队"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3f9b7371ac","type":"title","text":"再论革命的怀疑一切──砸碎形而上学的谬论","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e3d4df0d3","type":"paragraph","text":"“你们怀疑一切，就是怀疑党中央，怀疑毛主席！”","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57589a9cde","type":"paragraph","text":"同志，你冷静点好不好！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ae0d57e9f","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思提出“怀疑一切”，难道他会怀疑他自己所创建的马克思主义学说吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"583586ddba","type":"paragraph","text":"也许你们会说，“怀疑一切”，注意这是一切啊！","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e235ff2ec0","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要问：“共产党员对任何事情都要问一个为什么，……”注意这是“任何”啊！“任何”和“一切”岂有本质之异？按照你们的分析，这不是对党中央毛主席的指示也要问个“为什么”，也要“周密思考”，“绝对不应盲从”了！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e1b7c1500","type":"paragraph","text":"形而上学的先生们，你们是永远不会正确理解人类世界的！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebf33fc9aa","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：“事物矛盾的法则，即对立统一的法则，是自然和社会的根本法则，因而也是思维的根本法则。它是和形而上学的宇宙观相反的。它对于人类历史的认识史是一个大革命。”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bad9dde90b","type":"paragraph","text":"怀疑和相信，就是对立而又统一的。没有相信，就无所谓怀疑，没有怀疑，也就无所谓相信。怀疑是建立在相信真理的基础上，相信则是从怀疑之中引出的。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5bc270af18","type":"paragraph","text":"对于某个问题进行怀疑，无非是看一看这个问题到底是对还是不对，和真理相对照，是符合还是违背。不轻易相信，而要检验检验。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91eb9d328b","type":"paragraph","text":"对，还是不对，这必然要有一个客观标准。这个标准是什么呢？就是毛泽东主义。没有一个客观标准，怀疑是毫无意义的。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"724f1e6106","type":"paragraph","text":"既然，以毛泽东主义为客观标准，如何又能怀疑党中央、怀疑毛主席呢？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b85f8ca8a","type":"paragraph","text":"那末，你们怀疑不怀疑解放军？怀疑不怀疑大庆大寨？怀疑不怀疑三颗原子弹爆炸？一万二千吨水压机？雷锋、王杰、刘英俊？","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11e2ec36da","type":"paragraph","text":"这个问题倒是很天真！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5efa33ca1a","type":"paragraph","text":"既然，怀疑就是看一看它是对还是不对，其目的无非就是弄清其真相，那末达到这个目的之后，我们还怀疑什么呢？难道对于某个固定问题会永远怀疑下去吗？","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ad05bf225","type":"paragraph","text":"怀疑，就是要检验，凡是久经考验的，凡是已完全证明是真确的，就从怀疑之中引出了相信。我们对党中央，对毛主席无比的相信、无限敬仰、无限崇拜、无限热爱，又难道是凭空得出来的吗？解放军、大庆、大寨、雷锋、王杰、刘英俊，你们不认为它们是久经考验的吗？稍有常识的人，大概都会不言而喻了。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6295d95869","type":"paragraph","text":"“只有现在的和历史上的反动的统治阶级以及为他们服务的形而上学，不是把对立的事物当作生动的，有条件的，可变动的，互相转化的东西去看，而是当作死的，凝固的东西去看，并且把这种错误的东西到处宣传，迷惑人民群众，以达其继续统治的目的。共产党人的任务就在于揭露反动派和形而上学的错误思想，宣传事物的辩证法，促成事物的转化，达到革命的目的。”──摘自《矛盾论》","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa00703a6a","type":"paragraph","text":"更奇怪的是，竟然还有如此可笑之谈：","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a92e5c1f33","type":"paragraph","text":"“如果公安机关怀疑一切，那么就要把全国人民抓起来了！”","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"242b9ff6ca","type":"paragraph","text":"不动脑筋的人们难道你们不感到可悲可笑吗？","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"307fe114c8","type":"paragraph","text":"怀疑是具体的，并不是抽象的。有了问题才谈得到怀疑，凭空怎么能乱怀疑呢？怀疑是有根据的，怀疑绝不是无中生有！！怀疑的过程，是检验的过程，是调查研究的过程。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94fe34dfc3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：“你对那个问题不能解决吗？那末，你就去调查那个问题的现状和它的历史吧！你完完全全调查明白了，你对那个问题就有解决的办法了。一切结论产生于调查情况的末尾，而不是在它的先头。”","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"303d0913fe","type":"paragraph","text":"“怀疑一切是反动透顶了！”这是“王八蛋的怀疑一切！”","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a010fc67b2","type":"paragraph","text":"住口！！","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"724351085f","type":"paragraph","text":"绝不允许诬蔑、侮辱我们伟大的革命导师马克思！","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"464869ac39","type":"paragraph","text":"你们为何如此之恶？为什么偏要我们怀疑党中央和毛主席！！","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fc64adb94","type":"paragraph","text":"不是居心险恶，起码也是一个大糊涂虫！","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"514b93baab","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0d42e2a00","type":"paragraph","text":"形而上学的先生们，收回你们那一套吧！动动脑筋，冷静地思考思考。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d4ee0df1b","type":"paragraph","text":"×         ×        ×        ×         ×","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"27661540b5","type":"paragraph","text":"至于谩骂，无暇于此顾及了。还是送你们几句最高指示吧！","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"024d9ac3a1","type":"paragraph","text":"“鲁迅曾经批评过这种人，他说：‘辱骂和恐吓决不是战斗！’”","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f40118eda2","type":"paragraph","text":"──《反对党八股》","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"471c36391c","type":"paragraph","text":"“无论什么人，装腔作势借以吓人的方法，都是要不得的。因为这种吓人战术，对敌人毫无用处，对同志只有损害。这种吓人战术，是剥削阶级以及流氓无产者所惯用的手段，无产阶级不需要这类手段。”","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc68cfc7d1","type":"paragraph","text":"──《反对党八股》","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"59ecdc75fd","type":"paragraph","text":"清华大学东方红南下革命串联队先锋队","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be80ec8ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年九月十二日","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae51f5ac2c","type":"paragraph","text":"于昆明云大","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a245063cf2","type":"paragraph","text":"原载《清华大学大字报选编》","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4eed68d37b","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年10月7日","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fa0f6c2eeb","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}